projectGridLines.title: Slot booking portal for lab delivery
projectGridLines.description:
This portal will enable the student to book their lab slots according to

their flexible timelines and also eliminate the manual planning for the

lab delivery


Skills : Java script(React JS. Node JS),CSS, HTML and SQL
